data.description: Charming single story 3 bedroom 2 bath home located in a cul-de-sac in a quaint community with No HOA. Move in ready. Both bathrooms include shower and tub, new vanities and Moen faucets with lifetime warranty. Kitchen appliances are all newer stainless. Living room has original brick gas fireplace with custom mantel. Vaulted ceilings in living area, kitchen and master give a spacious feel. Updated windows and many ceiling fans to keep cooling costs low in summer months. Enjoy time watching movies on the outdoor living area on your enclosed private screened porch. Plenty of storage space in an out of home, with additional shed. Garage includes work bench, utility sink, new efficient tankless water heater and a bonus evaporative cooler. Bring your RV and toys, there is already an electric and sewer hook up. 3 paved driveways, RV gate on each side of home has paved drive that leads into backyard for extra parking. Location is convenient to shopping, restaurants and parks.
